1
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:38,440
=The Unbreakable Bond=
(Adapted from Xiao A'man's novel)

2
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:41,050
("After the Ugly Concubine Divorced,
She is Wooed By Big Shots of the Capital.")

3
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:44,100
=Episode 21=

4
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:48,760
My Lord, Eunuch Li is here.

5
00:00:51,180 --> 00:00:52,400
Good day, Eunuch Li.

6
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:58,679
Take it slow, Your Highness.

7
00:00:59,259 --> 00:01:00,120
Careful.

8
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:02,919
This lady is...

9
00:01:04,219 --> 00:01:05,919
It's because of my frail health.

10
00:01:06,619 --> 00:01:08,680
I heard First Young Lady Ling
is a skilled physician.

11
00:01:09,219 --> 00:01:11,359
So I came to the residence
to seek her help.

12
00:01:11,699 --> 00:01:12,919
Hence why I had to trouble you

13
00:01:13,139 --> 00:01:14,760
to bring my medicine
to the General's Residence.

14
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:19,040
You're being too courteous,
Your Highness.

15
00:01:19,059 --> 00:01:21,138
It's time to deliver

16
00:01:21,139 --> 00:01:23,120
your medicine anyway.

17
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:26,200
I wouldn't dare to keep you waiting.

18
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:29,179
If you didn't take the elixir
given by His Majesty on time,

19
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:31,040
that would be a problem.

20
00:01:43,419 --> 00:01:44,919
As expected from my brother's medicine.

21
00:01:46,419 --> 00:01:47,519
After taking it,

22
00:01:48,540 --> 00:01:50,639
I feel my strength coming back.

23
00:01:52,419 --> 00:01:54,919
I won't take up more
of Your Highness' time, then.

24
00:01:55,619 --> 00:01:57,639
Right, there's one more thing.

25
00:01:57,900 --> 00:02:00,120
His Majesty's birthday is coming up.

26
00:02:00,219 --> 00:02:03,480
Remember to return
to the palace

27
00:02:03,499 --> 00:02:05,320
to attend the banquet.

28
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,999
Yes, definitely.

29
00:02:08,659 --> 00:02:10,600
I will be there with gifts.

30
00:02:12,379 --> 00:02:13,200
Liefeng,

31
00:02:13,659 --> 00:02:15,040
see Eunuch Li out.

32
00:02:15,059 --> 00:02:15,799
Yes, my Lord.

33
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:22,799
Junye.

34
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:23,579
Junye.

35
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:24,799
Help me to my bed.

36
00:02:25,379 --> 00:02:26,119
Come.

37
00:02:31,779 --> 00:02:33,040
You knew it was poison.

38
00:02:33,659 --> 00:02:35,280
Why did you still drink it?

39
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:39,359
Now you know how difficult
my life has been

40
00:02:39,379 --> 00:02:40,839
over the years.

41
00:02:41,339 --> 00:02:44,040
Do they send the medicine
regularly for you to drink?

42
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:49,639
My brother has always been wary of me.

43
00:02:49,779 --> 00:02:51,519
But he's trying to kill you.

44
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:53,799
So be it.

45
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:55,639
Now you have me.

46
00:02:56,499 --> 00:02:58,119
I won't let anything happen to you.

47
00:02:58,860 --> 00:03:00,000
I know.

48
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:02,720
But we now have an opportunity.

49
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:06,200
We can enter the palace on account
of my brother's birthday celebration.

50
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:08,560
Then we'll sneak into the royal study.

51
00:03:10,219 --> 00:03:13,280
But I'm currently
not in the best condition.

52
00:03:13,379 --> 00:03:16,799
So I'm afraid you'll have
to do the work, Chuxia.

53
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:20,679
In order not to attract attention,

54
00:03:20,860 --> 00:03:22,760
you'll have to put on a disguise.

55
00:03:25,659 --> 00:03:28,079
You'll enter the palace
as my personal servant.

56
00:03:29,219 --> 00:03:30,320
We'll play it by ear.

57
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,560
I thought you'd not want to see me again

58
00:03:35,659 --> 00:03:36,839
after what happened.

59
00:03:37,219 --> 00:03:39,280
I'm not that petty of a person.

60
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:42,040
It's just that Father has been
planning for my wedding.

61
00:03:43,059 --> 00:03:44,679
You're set to marry?

62
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,720
Are you asking
about my future husband?

63
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:48,419
Or...

64
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:50,519
One move is not enough to show wisdom.

65
00:03:50,619 --> 00:03:52,560
One strum of the string
is not enough to express sadness.

66
00:03:53,379 --> 00:03:54,778
If I'm unable to give an answer,

67
00:03:54,779 --> 00:03:56,799
then I won't simply bring it up.

68
00:03:58,339 --> 00:03:59,859
But it's my utmost wish

69
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:01,239
for you to find happiness.

70
00:04:02,099 --> 00:04:04,498
People say life is like playing chess.

71
00:04:04,499 --> 00:04:05,799
No regrets after making a move.

72
00:04:06,339 --> 00:04:08,679
I enjoy playing chess with you

73
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:11,098
because I wish to learn
to cherish and let go.

74
00:04:11,099 --> 00:04:12,839
Know when to advance and retreat.

75
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:15,519
Princess,

76
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:18,000
you know my true feelings.

77
00:04:19,099 --> 00:04:20,479
So why bother?

78
00:04:27,099 --> 00:04:28,639
What's taking so long?

79
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:41,399
Are you pleased, Your Highness?

80
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:43,159
Very pleased.

81
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:46,200
Come on. We'll go some place
for you to practice.

82
00:04:46,339 --> 00:04:47,279
It's taken the bait!

83
00:04:48,099 --> 00:04:49,000
Stay quiet.

84
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,220
♪Neither burdening nor forgetting♪

85
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:56,300
♪At sunset, the sound of Zen echoes♪

86
00:04:57,500 --> 00:04:58,519
That's a big one.

87
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,440
Did you forget

88
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,159
I'm the lord again?

89
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,599
You're just my favourite servant.

90
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:09,560
Hand the fish to Liefeng.

91
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:22,039
♪Morning glows through the window
as I lazily get ready♪

92
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:27,460
♪Whose young lad is that,
sitting idly on the porch?♪

93
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:33,639
♪The spring of plum blossoms intoxicates,
apricot flowers bloom gold in the mist♪

94
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:39,340
♪Rain falls gently on banana leaves,
fish play beneath the lotus pads♪

95
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:42,540
♪Gazing at the green mountains,
they blend into the distant horizon♪

96
00:05:42,739 --> 00:05:43,800
I'm hungry.

97
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:48,119
♪Looking at the bright moon,
sending thoughts of longing♪

98
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,999
♪Neither burdening nor forgetting♪

99
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,980
♪At sunset, the sound of Zen echoes♪

100
00:05:55,979 --> 00:05:57,839
You're feeding me this?

101
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,479
♪Gazing at the green mountains,
they blend into the distant horizon♪

102
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:08,359
♪The wild geese call out,
sharing their heartfelt thoughts♪

103
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:11,340
♪Looking at the bright moon,
sending thoughts of longing♪

104
00:06:12,299 --> 00:06:13,839
The sun is blazing.

105
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:16,120
I can't open my eyes.

106
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:20,279
♪We share the long,
leisurely years together♪

107
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:22,079
♪Free and content♪

108
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:27,300
