is the beautiful springtime♪

109
00:06:38,020 --> 00:06:39,800
The fish isn't biting at all.

110
00:06:40,179 --> 00:06:41,599
I'm getting bored.

111
00:06:42,339 --> 00:06:44,599
Why don't you sing a song?

112
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:47,599
Your Highness.

113
00:06:49,179 --> 00:06:51,719
I'm only good with the sword.

114
00:06:52,659 --> 00:06:54,159
I can't sing.

115
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:56,839
Would you like to see?

116
00:06:59,179 --> 00:06:59,959
Forget it.

117
00:07:10,859 --> 00:07:13,320
I really put the foot in my mouth.

118
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:16,240
Why did I try to tease you

119
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:18,800
and make you pretend
to be my servant?

120
00:07:23,460 --> 00:07:24,320
Why?

121
00:07:24,659 --> 00:07:28,079
Are you not happy with my service?

122
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:29,680
Not at all.

123
00:07:30,419 --> 00:07:32,360
You're doing a terrific job.

124
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:36,200
It's just that I'm not meant
to enjoy the good treatment.

125
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:39,920
Go back and get changed.

126
00:07:40,099 --> 00:07:41,880
Later, we'll go to
the palace banquet together.

127
00:07:42,219 --> 00:07:43,240
I'll find a way

128
00:07:43,299 --> 00:07:44,959
to let you act on your own.

129
00:07:47,299 --> 00:07:49,320
Remember, safety first.

130
00:07:49,859 --> 00:07:51,599
Avoid direct confrontation
if anything happens.

131
00:07:55,979 --> 00:07:56,800
Junye.

132
00:07:58,820 --> 00:08:01,120
When we find out the truth,

133
00:08:03,299 --> 00:08:04,719
let's leave this place.

134
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:06,560
You can be the lackadaisical prince.

135
00:08:07,299 --> 00:08:08,800
And I'll be the lackadaisical princess.

136
00:08:09,739 --> 00:08:10,760
That's for sure.

137
00:08:11,779 --> 00:08:12,819
But right now,

138
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:14,639
we have other things to take care of.

139
00:08:17,219 --> 00:08:18,079
You're right.

140
00:08:20,099 --> 00:08:23,200
The residual poison in your body
hasn't been cleared.

141
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:24,599
Don't worry.

142
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:27,000
It's only a banquet.

143
00:08:27,659 --> 00:08:28,680
I can handle it.

144
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:45,160
Uncle is here to attend
Father's birthday banquet, right?

145
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:47,379
But it looks like

146
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,959
you have good news to share.

147
00:08:49,659 --> 00:08:51,520
I don't mind telling you, Uncle.

148
00:08:51,659 --> 00:08:52,818
Father

149
00:08:52,819 --> 00:08:54,879
will be nominating me
as the Crown Prince.

150
00:08:55,459 --> 00:08:56,640
More importantly,

151
00:08:56,699 --> 00:08:59,320
he will once more bequeath
Chuxia to me.

